Package controller

Class Controller

java.lang.Object
controller.Controller
All Implemented Interfaces:
IControllerMtoV, IControllerVtoM
public class Controller extends Object implements IControllerVtoM, IControllerMtoV
The Controller class serves as the intermediary between the view and the model, handling communication and control flow for the simulation.
